'''盧西亞諾龍屬'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Lucianosaurus''）是[[羊膜動物|羊膜動物]]的一[[屬|屬]]，可能是分類未定的[[主龍形類|主龍形類]]動物<ref name=irmis2006>{{Cite journal|author=Irmis, R.B., Parker, W.G., Nesbitt, S.J., and Liu, J.|year=2006|title=Early ornithischian dinosaurs: the Triassic record|journal=Historical Biology|volume=iFirst article|pages=1-20|id=DOI: 10.1080/08912960600719988}}</ref>。牠的[[化石|化石]]只有[[牙齒|牙齒]]，發現於[[美國|美國]][[新墨西哥州|新墨西哥州]]的[[三疊紀|三疊紀]]晚期地層。[[模式種|模式種]]是''L. wildi''，是由[[阿德里安·亨特|阿德里安·亨特]]（Adrian Hunt）及[[斯潘塞·盧卡斯|斯潘塞·盧卡斯]]（Spencer G. Lucas）在1994年描述及命名的<ref name=hunt1994>{{Cite book|author=A. P. Hunt and S. G. Lucas|year=1994|chapter=Ornithischian dinosaurs from the Upper Triassic of the United States|editor=N. C. Fraser & H.-D. Sues (eds.)|title=In the Shadow of the Dinosaurs: Early Mesozoic Tetrapods|publisher=Cambridge University Press|location=Cambridge|pages=227-241}}</ref>。盧西亞諾龍的屬名是以其發現地來命名<ref>http://geonames.usgs.gov/pls/gnispublic/f?p=gnispq:3:::NO::P3_FID:898818</ref>。

==分類及命名==
盧西亞諾龍最初被分類為[[鳥臀目|鳥臀目]][[恐龍|恐龍]]<ref name=hunt1994/>。由於牠只有[[牙齒|牙齒]][[化石|化石]]，[[大衛·諾曼|大衛·諾曼]]（David B. Norman）等人在2004年認為牠只是[[疑名|疑名]]<ref name=norman2004>{{Cite book|author=D. B. Norman, L. M. Witmer, and D. B. Weishampel|year=2004|chapter=Basal Ornithischia|editor=D. B. Weishampel, H. Osmólska, and P. Dodson (eds.)|title=The Dinosauria|url=https://archive.org/details/dinosauriandedit00weis|edition=2nd edition|publisher=University of California Press|location=Berkeley|pages=[https://archive.org/details/dinosauriandedit00weis/page/325 325]-334}}</ref>。在2007年，Sterling Nesbitt等人認為牠是有效的屬，並將牠重新分類在[[主龍形類|主龍形類]]之下<ref name=nesbitt2007>{{Cite journal|author=S. J. Nesbitt, R. B. Irmis, and W. G. Parker|year=2007|title=A critical re-evaluation of the Late Triassic dinosaur taxa of North America|journal=Journal of Systematic Palaeontology|volume=5|issue=2|pages=209-243}}</ref>。另一群科學家也將盧西亞諾龍歸類為主龍形類的分類未定屬<ref name="irmis06">Irmis, R.B., Parker, W.G., Nesbitt, S.J., and Liu, J. (2006). Early ornithischian dinosaurs: the Triassic record. ''Historical Biology'' '''19'''(1):3-22. {{doi|10.1080/08912960600719988}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thescelosaurus.com/dinosauromorpha.htm |title=Dinosaurs |work=Thescelosaurus.com |author=Tweet, J. |year=2010 |publisher= |page= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090727131406/http://www.thescelosaurus.com/dinosauromorpha.htm |archivedate=2009-07-27 }}</ref>。近年被發現牙齒跟橫齒獸科有高度相似處，例如：近三角形齒冠、加大的鋸齒邊緣、牙齒位於齒槽。另有研究人員指出，根據地理分布，特髏龍比較可能屬於主龍形類，而非較侷限性的橫齒獸科<ref>{{Cite journal|author=Christian F. Kammerer, John J. Flynn, Lovasoa Ranivoharimanana and André R. Wyss |year=2012 |title=Ontogeny in the Malagasy Traversodontid ''Dadadon isaloi'' and a Reconsideration of its Phylogenetic Relationships |journal=Fieldiana Life and Earth Sciences |volume=5 |pages=112–125 |doi=10.3158/2158-5520-5.1.112}}</ref>。

